From a JIRA customer:

{quote}
When importing issues from our legacy system to a project, I select the project, then when mapping the statuses I'm offered all possible statuses, even though they're not all handled on the workflow scheme for the target project. Getting this wrong resulted in errors for all records where the mapping was to an invalid status, but the error message gave absolutely no indication that this was the problem. So, please: Either don't offer mappings to invalid statuses, or: Provide an error message that tells me this was the problem. Because it took me a while, and a fair bit of frustration, to figure this one out.
{quote}

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
